{
  "texts": [
    "In hospitals, RAG technology can integrate nursing experiences from various hospitals with LLMs and provide personalized care recommendations.",
    "From a technological development perspective, RAG technology should evolve towards multimodal fusion, incorporating nursing videos, images, and textual information to further enhance the support for nursing-related tasks.",
    "In summary, the present study evaluated the application of RAG technology to LLMs in breast cancer care, providing a theoretical foundation for the clinical use of RAG technology and offering technical insights into the development of specialized LLMs for nursing.",
    "This study revealed that RAG technology could significantly improve LLM performance for breast cancer nursing care.",
    "This improvement is likely due to the increased accuracy of answers without diminishing empathy."
  ]
}